These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, peas, watermelon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, scientific, horror
1. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating peas##1
2. the person eating watermelon is between the person watching horror movies and the person eating peas##2
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Food      | peas | watermelon | strawberry |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | adventure    | horror   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, basketball
There 3 different types of food: peas, nectarine, grapes
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person eating grapes is between the person eating peas and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Sport   | baseball    | basketball        | climbing |
| Food     | nectarine | grapes | peas         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, accountant, dancer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, jazz, pop
1. the fan metal is on the right of the musician##1
2. the musician is between the fan jazz and the dancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Job   | accountant | musician     | dancer |
| Music-Genre        | jazz  | pop | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, peas, artichoke
House: tower, gothic-revival, art-deco
1. the person eating radish is the tower house##1
2. the person eating artichoke is between the gothic-revival house and the tower house##2
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Food   | peas  | artichoke     | radish |
| House           | gothic-revival | art-deco | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, game
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, project-manager, electrician
1. the game-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the electrician##1
3. the police-officer is between the electrician and the project-manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | game     | aristoff |
| Job     | electrician    | police-officer | project-manager    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, jet-ski
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, hiking, photography
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | subway   | jet-ski        |
| Hobby         | hiking | writing | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, train, quad-bike
House: futuristic, palace, art-deco
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the futuristic house is between the person driving the quad-bike and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Transport          | train  | taxi  | quad-bike |
| House   | palace | futuristic | art-deco     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, dannemann
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking soy-milk##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | cola  | hot-chocolate  |
| Cigar   | bolivar | alhambra | dannemann |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, september
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, baking, camping
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Birthday       | september | june | may  |
| Hobby   | camping    | singing        | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, chinchilla
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, dannemann
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the dannemann-smoker and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | bird | goldfish |
| Cigar   | dannemann     | baccarat    | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, aconite
City: venice, boston, rome
1. the person traveling to rome is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person traveling to venice##2
2. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | tulip      | aconite      |
| City       | boston  | rome | venice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, social-worker, police-officer
3 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret, bird
1. the social-worker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the fisherman is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Job   | fisherman | social-worker   | police-officer   |
| Pet         | ferret | bird | turtle |

