1. the thai is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the egyptian is between the malaysian and the bluemaster-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |     3     |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | game  | ritmeester       |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | malaysian |

