.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, metal, house
House: ranch-style, futuristic, tower
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan trance##1
2. the ranch-style house is between the fan metal and the tower house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | trance   | house  |
