.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, chaman, tiparillo
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, sudoku, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the chaman-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar   | chaman | game   | tiparillo   |
| Hobby         | dancing  | singing | sudoku |

