.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, dressmaker, police-officer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, aconite
1. the paramedic is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the dressmaker is between the police-officer and the person who growsbegonia##2
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Job      | police-officer | dressmaker   | paramedic |
| Flower   | aconite  | rose | begonia   |

 